<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men gē chàng, wǒ men gē chàng, yé hé huá zuò wáng le.
 wǒ men zàn měi, wǒ men zàn měi, yé hé huá zuò wáng le.
 wǒ men hū hǎn, wǒ men hū hǎn, yé hé huá zuò wáng le.
 wǒ men gē chàng, wǒ men gē chàng, de shàng de rén dōu tīng jiàn.
 wǒ men zàn měi, wǒ men zàn měi, xiǎng biàn tiān de zhī jiān.
 wǒ men hū hǎn, wǒ men hū hǎn, zhèn dòng dà shān hé xiǎo shān.</lyrics>
<title>yé hé huá zuò wáng le 迦南80</title>
<hymn_number>80</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
